text: Hai Miyamaratiyaya! Lidasun niyo so manga ginawa niyo go so taalok rukano ko Apoi a aya itagon niyan na so manga Manosiya a go so manga Ator, a pakisisiyap ko manga Malaikat a manga babasung, a manga babagur, di ran shangkaan so Allah ko Sogowan Niyan kiran, go ing-gogolalan niran so Ipushogo kiran
